<br>
<br>
This is the whole benefit to having a firepet.  Mana efficency.  I'm not fighting against my pet to get all the exp, so i dont have to nuke 2 times unless i need to.  And i dont have to recast a DS on the pet, which saves a TON of downtime considering the right camps.<br>
<br>
Sure, sometimes you can find comparable alternative pets for situations...but why would you ever skimp on the side of being efficent?<br>
